name: skate, oil & ladder the game
description:
awkward adventure skate series 10/50.

here's O & Bzjm & the Geng Gerimis crews fave game: snake & ladder but their own version.

originally the idea of this artwork is the merchandise i made for hani & robert's (h&r) with o & bzjm characters back in 2001. 20 years later i decided make it again but with new touch & approach.

drawing pen on paper with digital coloring.

december 2021.
